    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are 19 year old Tyrone Watermelon -- ambitious paranormal investigator and convenience store clerk, eager for a big break. When you receive a call from a man calling himself Roane Vaydich asking you to investigate his haunted house, you are ecstatic. Finally, a chance to get your name out there!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of your perilous journey lies a <strong><i>fat </i></strong>paycheck -- $25.99, to be exact -- enough to kickstart your career, or maybe even pay off that old guy that sold you those funny-looking brownies the other day...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But these ghosts are different... spooki<strong>er</strong>... scari<strong>er</strong>... retarded<strong>er</strong>...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five Nights at Roner's: Remastered is a ground-up recreation of the original game, which was made in three days. This remake brings it up to the standard set by Five Nights at Roner's 2, which was made in six months. Complete with a full visual overhaul, several gameplay improvements/additions, and a (finally) coherent story, Five Nights at Roner's has never been better...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, without further ado, can you survive...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FIVE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NIGHTS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RONER'S?</strong></p>",
